WEBVTT

00:10:27.414 --> 00:10:30.685
This is my great friend 
Harry from Puerto Rico.

00:10:30.685 --> 00:10:31.928
And Natalia.

00:10:31.928 --> 00:10:35.591
She and I started 
the first albinism society in Russia.

00:10:35.591 --> 00:10:39.726
Maizan and her sister 
and mom in Malaysia.

00:10:39.726 --> 00:10:42.725
Ceara. All she ever wanted to do 
was be a dancer.

00:10:42.725 --> 00:10:44.841
She was told that 
because of her visual impairment,

00:10:44.841 --> 00:10:46.217
she'll never dance.

00:10:46.217 --> 00:10:49.283
She'll never be able to follow 
the choreography or the dance steps.

00:10:49.283 --> 00:10:53.804
She's like, they said, 
find another love, another passion.

00:10:53.804 --> 00:10:55.221
She's like, no.

00:10:55.221 --> 00:10:57.367
She's New Zealand's Celtic dance champion,

00:10:57.367 --> 00:11:00.647
and just started a school for dance 
for kids with visual impairment.